= XiZero =

== Version: ==

0.1 - Callbox

== Install: ==

./smmn
./smmn install #requires root 

== Dependencies: ==

- xsltproc

== Usage: ==

``xizero``	#start game
``unit``	#model viewer and benchmark

== Changelog: ==


== Features: ==

=== Major: ===

- Software Rasterizer
- Flatshading
- Blinn Shadows
- Emissive Glow
- 2xFSAA
- FSMB

=== Minor: ===

- 32bit Z-Buffer
- Cordic Fixed Point Math
- No Floating Point Operations
- Minimal Branching
- Minimal Dependencies
- Only human readable, non-binary, data
- Framebuffer (independence from X,Wayland,OpenGL,DirectFB)
- Dyadic Explosions

== Bugs: ==

- Mouse / Joypad Support
- Intel GMAs need video=800x600

== Warning: ==

XiZero is still in ALPHA stage, so do not expect it to work error- and bug-free.

